	     <tr><td id=headerrow colspan=2 class=mform valign=top><a name=classes.html?class=2&mid=102526755023891>&nbsp;</a><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=2&mid=102526755023891>RE: dual wielding</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=2&mid=102526755023891#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a>
	     <br clear=all><small>Posted @ Fri, Jun 28th 8:42 AM 2002</small></td></tr>
	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=61546><span id=Sage>Slipskin</span></a><br><b><span id=Sage>Sage</span></b><br><span id=notbold>1090 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [3.31]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>No, there is no button for dual wield. You just put a weapon in both your melee slots and leave it alone.&nbsp;&nbsp;Dual wield will happen all by itself at the appropriate time.  When you first start with dual wield it won't happen much at all.  Just be very patient and over the next 4 or 5 levels you will see it happen more frequently.  You will not see a message that specifically states dual wield being used - except for the skill up message.  What you will see is 2 attack messages where you only saw 1 before.  <br><br>One way to tell one attack from the other is to put a different weapon in each hand.  Bare fist and blunt weapons will give a message like<br><br>You strike at a &lt;monster name&gt; and miss!<br><br>Slashing weapons and piercing weapons will replace the word &quot;strike&quot; with a word unique for that weapon type.  That way you know which weapon the attack used - the main hand or the seconday hand.  Dual wield will always be the weapon in the secondary hand (or melee slot).<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Fri Jun 28 08:36:12 2002</em></p>&nbsp;<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=104222" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=104222</a><br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=479760" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=479760</a></td></td></tr>
